dolly is a tool to create a clone of a hierarchy of ZFS. It is based on
snapshots, clone command and python. For more info : check the README_DOLLY

tzm-sched allow you to backup zfs hierarchy with dsmc sched using snapshots
(clone of this snapshot in fact).
Check the README_TZM_SCHED

If you find this script useful, consider a recommendation on LinkedIn with my
email briner@infomaniak.ch. :)
